=== questionnaire plugin 0.0.1

This is a questionnaire/survey plugin for Chiliproject.

ONLY compatible with Chiliproject 3.X NOT compatible with Chiliproject 2.X


== Getting the plugin

The newest version is always at {GitHub}[http://github.com/kwanko/chiliproject_questionnaires].


=== Feature

1. Set for each project users who can add or validate a questionnaire before publication

2. Ask questions and request users to answer it

3. Consult the user answers


=== Plugin installation

1. Copy the plugin directory(chiliproject_questionnaires) into the vendor/plugins directory
   NOTE: The plugin directory must be chiliproject_questionnaires!

2. Migrate plugin:
   rake db:migrate_plugins NAME=chiliproject_questionnaires RAILS_ENV=production

3. Start Chiliproject

4. Grant add_questionnaire right to users who will create questionnaire and valid_questionnaire right to user in charge of the validation of questionnaire


